=== 哺乳類 ===
[[File:Rhino_sizes_English.png|thumb]]（深灰色）與其他犀牛和人類的體型比較（但也有研究認為[[納瑪象|納瑪象]]才是體型最大的陸上哺乳動物）]]
[[藍鯨|藍鯨]]為目前已知體型最大的[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]，目前最長體長紀錄為{{convert|29.9|m}}<ref name=Sears_Calamb_2002>{{cite book | last1=Sears | first1=R. | last2=Calambokidis | first2=J. | title=Update COSEWIC status report on the blue whale (''Balaenoptera musculus'') in Canada | location=Ottawa, ON | publisher=[[Committee_on_the_Status_of_Endangered_Wildlife_in_Canada|Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada]] | page=32 | date=2002}}</ref> ，體重則可達{{convert|199|t}}<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sizing ocean giants: patterns of intraspecific size variation in marine megafauna|url=https://peerj.com/articles/715|last=McClain|first=Craig R.|last2=Balk|first2=Meghan A.|date=2015-01-13|journal=PeerJ|doi=10.7717/peerj.715|volume=3|pages=e715|language=en|issn=2167-8359|pmc=PMC4304853|pmid=25649000|last3=Benfield|first3=Mark C.|last4=Branch|first4=Trevor A.|last5=Chen|first5=Catherine|last6=Cosgrove|first6=James|last7=Dove|first7=Alistair D.M.|last8=Gaskins|first8=Leo|last9=Helm|first9=Rebecca R.|access-date=2021-11-17|archive-date=2021-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223225547/https://peerj.com/articles/715/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

現存體型最大的陸上哺乳動物為[[非洲草原象|非洲草原象]]，肩高達{{convert|3.96|m|ft|1|abbr=on}}，體重約可達{{convert|10.4|MT|ST|abbr=on|}}<ref name="probos_mass">{{Cite journal|title=Proboscideans: Shoulder Height, Body Mass and Shape|url=http://www.app.pan.pl/article/item/app001362014.html|last=Larramendi|first=Asier|date=2015|journal=Acta Palaeontologica Polonica|doi=10.4202/app.00136.2014|s2cid=2092950|access-date=2021-11-17|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522153856/http://www.app.pan.pl/article/item/app001362014.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。已滅絕體型最大的陸上哺乳動物則認為是[[巨犀屬|巨犀]]，為現存[[犀牛|犀牛]]的近親，推估肩高可達{{convert|4.8|m|ft|1|abbr=on}}，體長超過{{convert|7.4|m|ft|1|abbr=on}}，體重可達17公噸<ref name=probos_mass/><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The largest land mammal ever imagined|url=https://academic.oup.com/zoolinnean/article-lookup/doi/10.1111/j.1096-3642.1993.tb02560.x|last=Fortelius|first=Mikael|last2=Kappelman|first2=John|date=1993-05|journal=Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1096-3642.1993.tb02560.x|volume=108|pages=85–101|language=en|access-date=2021-11-17|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303061125/https://academic.oup.com/zoolinnean/article-lookup/doi/10.1111/j.1096-3642.1993.tb02560.x|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，一項研究認為[[長鼻目|長鼻目]]的[[納瑪象|納瑪象]]擁有比巨犀更大的體型，根據腿骨化石的分析推測，納瑪象個體的體重最高可能達22公噸<ref name="probos_mass" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/66361/ancient-elephant-may-have-been-biggest-land-mammal-ever|title=An Ancient Elephant May Have Been Biggest Land Mammal Ever|date=2015-07-17|access-date=2017-04-21|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227042915/https://www.mentalfloss.com/article/66361/ancient-elephant-may-have-been-biggest-land-mammal-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
