===軟體動物===
[[File:Giant_squid_melb_aquarium03.jpg|thumb]]]]
最大型的軟體動物與最大型的無脊椎動物（以體重來說）均為[[大王酸漿魷|大王酸漿魷]]<ref>[http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2007/02/070222-squid-pictures.html Photo in the News: Colossal Squid Caught off Antarctica] {{Wayback|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2007/02/070222-squid-pictures.html |date=20171213173004 }}. News.nationalgeographic.com (2010-10-28)</ref>，根據目前發現的標本，估計其最大體長可達{{convert|12|to|14|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重則達{{convert|750|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.unmuseum.org/colossalsquid.htm|title=The UnMuseum - The Colossal Squid|website=www.unmuseum.org|accessdate=14 June 2017|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126043020/http://www.unmuseum.org/colossalsquid.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年，紐西蘭當局宣稱他們捕捉到目前已知最大隻的大王酸漿魷，長{{convert|10|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重約{{convert|450|kg|lb|abbr=on}}。經過之後的測量後修正為體長{{convert|4.2|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重為{{convert|495|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name="NZ_Herald_10430435">Kathy Marks. [http://www.nzherald.co.nz/section/1/story.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10430435 NZ's colossal squid to be microwaved] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/section/1/story.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10430435 |date=20070929125549 }}. [[新西兰先驱报|The New Zealand Herald]] (2007-03-23)</ref>，其[[外套膜|外套膜]]長度為{{convert|2.5|m|ft|abbr=on}}。

在大王酸漿魷被發現之前，[[巨烏賊|巨烏賊]]曾經被認為是體型最大的魷魚；相較於大王酸漿魷，巨烏賊擁有較小的外套膜以及較長的觸手，因此加上觸手的長度巨烏賊的體長仍然能夠超過大王酸漿魷。1878年，一隻巨烏賊的屍體被沖上[[紐芬蘭島|紐芬蘭島]]，總長（從外套膜頂端至最長的觸手末端）達{{convert|18|m|ft|abbr=on}}，外套膜與頭部部分長度為{{convert|6.1|m|ft|abbr=on}}，外套膜最厚的部位直徑可達{{convert|4.6|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重超過{{convert|900|kg|lb|abbr=on}}。這個樣本如今仍然經常被引述為目前已知體型最大的無脊椎動物<ref name = "Wood"/><ref>[http://marinebio.org/species.asp?id=156 Giant Squids, Architeuthis dux] {{Wayback|url=http://marinebio.org/species.asp?id=156 |date=20080206200618 }}. Marinebio.org</ref><ref>[http://animals.nationalgeographic.com/animals/invertebrates/giant-squid/ Giant Squid, Giant Squid Pictures, Giant Squid Facts] {{Wayback|url=http://animals.nationalgeographic.com/animals/invertebrates/giant-squid/ |date=20110921094625 }}. Animals.nationalgeographic.com (2006-12-04)</ref>。然而，這些數據並沒有非常正式的紀錄，且巨烏賊專家{{link-en|史特夫·奧沙|Steve O'Shea}}認為這樣的體長可能是透過將觸手像橡皮筋那樣拉長才可能測量到的<ref name=OShea>O'Shea, S. 2003. [http://www.tonmo.com/science/public/giantsquidfacts.php "Giant Squid and Colossal Squid Fact Sheet".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tonmo.com/science/public/giantsquidfacts.php |date=20161117175518 }} The Octopus News Magazine Online.</ref>。

